######## elaborate-changes.soar ######

Rules to detect changes on the input-link 
	that have to do with the robot. 

# Change: changed-arm-status
	type changed-arm-status
	category robot
	op-name attend-to-changed-arm-status
	self-info <self> # io.input-link.self

	Compares the world.robot.arm.moving-state << moving stopped >> 
		with input-link.self.arm.moving-state << moving stopped >>

# Change: changed-moving-state
	type changed-moving-state
	category robot
	op-name attend-to-changed-moving-state
	self-info <self> # io.input-link.self

	Compares the world.robot.moving-state << moving stopped >>
		with input-link.self.moving-state << moving stopped >>

# Change: changed-waypoint
	type changed-waypoint
	category robot
	op-name attend-to-changed-waypoint
	new-waypoint-handle <wp-handle>

	Compares the world.robot.current-waypoint.handle <wp-handle>
		with input-link.self.current-waypoint.waypoint-handle <wp-handle>

